<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Settings</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/main.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div>Settings</div>
        <div><a href="/">Console</a></div>
    </div>
    <form action="/save-settings" method="POST">
        <label for="directoryPath">Directory Path:</label>
        <input type="text" id="directoryPath" name="directoryPath" value="<%= directoryPath %>">
        <br/>
        <p>This is the command executed when you press Run Test button. The command should be the same you run from the root of your system (not relative path), <b>@yourTag</b> is a placeholder and will be replaced by the tag selected by the user</p>
        <p>For example: mvn clean test -Pselenium-regression-tests '-Dcucumber.filter.tags=@yourTag'</p>
        <label for="testCommand">Run command:</label>
        <input type="text" id="testCommand" name="testCommand" value="<%= testCommand %>">
        <br/>
        <label for="folderToExclude">Folder to exclude:</label>
        <input type="text" id="folderToExclude" name="folderToExclude" value="<%= folderToExclude %>">
        <input type="submit" value="Save">
    </form>
    <a href="/">Back to home</a>
</body>
</html>